{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About The World</h2><br>As you receive a letter from an old friend begging for help, you jump onto the first train headed towards his town only to find out that he has disappeared, and he\u2019s not the only one.<br><br>Immerse yourself in this community, its clans and their secrets, the projects they protects.<br><br>Use all the tools you can find and flex your creativity, track your friend down and prevent disaster.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/TrainStation_Description_Screenshot.png?t=1667963402\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>User-interface free, this immersive simulation encourages the player to explore, analyze and interact with the world to progress through the adventure.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/Keypad_Description_Screenshot.png?t=1667963402\" /><br><br></li><li>Explore this town freely, each neighborhood holds its own secrets.<br></li><li>Each hand can be independently controlled to pick up, inspect, move, use, destroy, throw or craft.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/EmployeList_Description_Screenshot.png?t=1667963402\" /><br><br></li><li>You can interact with almost everything you see. Some objects are useful some are not.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/GrabHelmet_Description_Screenshot.png?t=1667963402\" /><br><br></li><li>Carefully consider what to hold on to. With just two hands and a small backpack, what you choose to leave behind is a matter of life and death.<br></li><li>Interact with &quot;people&quot; of the town. Show them an item and see what they have to say.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/ShowPicture_Description_Screenshot.png?t=1667963402\" /><br><br></li><li>Each situation you face can be solved multiple ways.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/PlankPuzzle_Description_Screenshot.png?t=1667963402\" /><br><br></li><li>Sleuth in daylight or lurk through the night. The challenges you face may change with the sun, but danger is always present.<br><br>                                 <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/Forest_axe.png?t=1667963402\" /></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1667963402","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1667963402","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1667963402","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1667963402","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About The World</h2><br>As you receive a letter from an old friend begging for help, you jump onto the first train headed towards his town only to find out that he has disappeared, and he\u2019s not the only one.<br><br>Immerse yourself in this community, its clans and their secrets, the projects they protects.<br><br>Use all the tools you can find and flex your creativity, track your friend down and prevent disaster.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1980140/extras/TrainStation_Description_Screenshot.png?t=